---
title: Cancel Reservation - Activity Diagram
---
flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Select reservation from table]
    B --> C[Click Cancel Selected]
    C --> D{Reservation selected?}
    D -->|No| E[Display warning: Select a reservation]
    E --> Z([End])
    D -->|Yes| F[Show confirmation dialog]
    F --> G{User confirms?}
    G -->|No| Z
    G -->|Yes| H{Already cancelled?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Display error: Already cancelled]
    I --> Z
    H -->|No| J[Set status to CANCELLED]
    J --> K[Restore seats to train]
    K --> L[Save to DataStore]
    L --> M[Display success message]
    M --> N[Refresh tables]
    N --> Z

    style A fill:#009688,color:#fff
    style Z fill:#dc3545,color:#fff
    style D fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style G fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style H fill:#ffc107,color:#000
    style J fill:#19376d,color:#fff
    style M fill:#28a745,color:#fff
